runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

playstore_details.title: CoinTopper - Cryptocurrency, ICOs, News & Guides
playstore_details.description:
Curious about cryptocurrencies? If yes, CoinTopper App is certainly for you!

CoinTopper is an app that tracks cryptocurrency market data in real-time. Track the price fluctuations, market volume, real-time charts and discover numerous other features by installing the app. Get live data of Bitcoin, Ether, Ripple, Monero and 1500+ coins with a single tap. You can also add your favourite coins to Watchlist and even set alerts and get notified about the variations on your selected cryptocurrencies. Give it a try and am sure you'll love it.

Features

The features of CoinTopper sets it apart from other crypto apps and you will find the reasons below:

- Search among 1500+ coins listed on our app and get the real-time data of any cryptocurrency

- Add your favourite cryptocurrencies to a separate list called 'Watchlist' and track their updates regularly

- Create push notifications that alert you to price highs and lows, or daily or weekly updates. Easily set your priority custom alerts.

- Real-time charts with detailed price variations and timeline to track the cryptocurrency performance over the time.

- Stay up to date with the Current and historical trends for all the digital tokens in the market.

- Share price info, charts, volume, etc of any cryptocurrency on your social media channels by downloading or sharing the 'Snapshot' which is readily available for you to obtain the statistics in one frame.

- The application allows you to set any fiat currency as Base currency like USD, EURO, INR, etc to compare the prices in your native currency

*ICO:* CoinTopper encourages new innovations and love to take such innovations to the public. In the Crypto world, there are plenty of coins and tokens rising up everyday. So, we at CoinTopper have introduced the ICO Launchpad providing the analysis and research of ICO. We have our own rating methodology that we use to filter out the most genuine projects where the ICOs are classified in various categories like upcoming, live, featured, etc as per their respective calender ICO period. Visit our "ICO" section to Browse ICOs and if you want to submit one, go ahead and submit your ico https://cointopper.com/submit-ico


*Guide:* CoinTopper believes that its extremely crucial to educate oneself on the day-to-day happenings in the financial and technological world. To fulfill this, we have come up with a very interesting section in our website that's called "Guides". We are continuously updating this section to cover every jargon and topic of the Blockchain and Crypto Space. Visit our "Guides" section to know more.

*News:* Digital world is growing its wings at the speed of light. And with the advent of technology like Blockchain and digital currencies rising up. Being aware about it is a must. So here we are with the "News" section, offering the latest feeds, trends, breakthroughs, inventions and analysis. To stay updated with the World 2.0. Stay tuned to our "News" section.

Airdrop: CoinTopper has also launched the Airdrop section, featuring the ICO Airdrop List where you can earn free coins and tokens of various ICOs by participating in their Airdrop programs available on CoinTopper. To know more, visit the "Airdrops" section.

and much more in the app!

Enjoy!!
